00:13:15.121 --> 00:13:16.099
Permisi.

00:13:20.330 --> 00:13:21.345
Hai!

00:13:22.617 --> 00:13:23.879
Saya Monty.

00:13:24.542 --> 00:13:25.711
Monty Bajwa.

00:13:38.143 --> 00:13:39.315
Dan saya lajang.

